CacheMode: Cache mode, whether disabled, playing or recording
TargetCache: The cache to target when recording or playing
ReverseCacheBeginTime: Cache mode, whether disabled, playing or recording
SaveCollisionData: Whether to buffer collisions during recording
DoGenerateCollisionData: Whether to generate collisions during playback
CollisionDataSizeMax: Maximum size of the collision buffer
CollisionDataSpatialHashRadius: Spatial hash radius for collision data
MaxCollisionPerCell: Maximum number of collisions per cell
SaveBreakingData: Whether to buffer breakings during recording
DoGenerateBreakingData: Whether to generate breakings during playback
BreakingDataSizeMax: Maximum size of the breaking buffer
BreakingDataSpatialHashRadius: Spatial hash radius for breaking data
MaxBreakingPerCell: Maximum number of breaking per cell
SaveTrailingData: Whether to buffer trailings during recording
DoGenerateTrailingData: Whether to generate trailings during playback
TrailingDataSizeMax: Maximum size of the trailing buffer
